title: The Trendhouse of Horror 10/25: Jon Stewart, Treehouse of Horror, Dr. Oz, Brittney Griner, Kevin Bacon, COVID
itunes:title: The Trendhouse of Horror 10/25: Jon Stewart, Treehouse of Horror, Dr. Oz, Brittney Griner, Kevin Bacon, COVID
description:
In this edition of The Trendhouse of Horror, Jack and Miles discuss Jon Stewart's latest interview with Mark Brnovich, the best 'The Treehouse of Horror' episodes, the Oz vs. Fetterman, Brittney Griner getting sentenced to 9 years in a Russian penal colony, Kevin Bacon entering the MCU, and the apparent media blackout on the new COVID booster!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
